      • getConfidenceIntervalHalfSpan

        public double getConfidenceIntervalHalfSpan(double alpha)
        Get the half space (single side) of the confidence interval for the bootstrap analysis. The full confidence interval range is the mean minus the half space to the mean plus the half space.
        Parameters:
        alpha - the significance level for the confidence interval (typically, 0.05, etc.).
        Returns:
        a positive floating-point value.
